  "title": "Citrusy Crisp Middle Eastern Goats Cheese Bake",
  "description": "A refreshing and flavorful dish featuring tangy goats cheese, the crunch of pine nuts, and the zing of citrus, all in a salt-baked crust.",
  "cuisine": "Middle Eastern",
