  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Line a baking dish with parchment paper.",
    "In a bowl, mix together goats cheese, pine nuts, parsley, lemon zest, and lemon juice.",
    "Transfer the mixture to the prepared baking dish, leaving a 1-inch border around the edges.",
    "Sprinkle coarse salt over the cheese mixture.",
    "Bake for 20 minutes, or until the cheese is lightly browned and the crust is crispy.",
    "Remove from oven and let cool slightly before serving."
